title: HUGE! Classic, lovely quiet, tree lined with easy Commute!
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 48335489', 'Rent: $1,750 / Month', 'Beds: 2', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 09/01/2022', 'Pet: No Pets', 'Parking:: street parking', 'Amazingly Green, Tree Lined but quiet location right across from a large park.', 'Super ease of commute using one of the many bus lines right across the street or Short walk to the West Medford Train Station', 'Classic, Huge Apartment!', 'Dining Room, Living Room, Den, Sun Parlor, Two Large Bedrooms, Eat-in Kitchen, Pantry, Nice upper floor Porch.', 'Two large bedrooms w/great closet space.', 'Great Space to enjoy!', 'Lovely dining room for dinners.', 'Living room, plus Den and One large Enclosed porch as well as One outdoor porch as well.', 'Kitchen w/lots of space and a great Pantry!!', 'This is a Steal.', 'MUST See this GREAT apartment.', '****NOTE: No Laundry in the Building.', 'Laundromat right in West Medford Square w/IN .4', 'Mi of the House!', 'Laundry pick up and drop off service available as well.', 'No Dishwasher in the Kitchen.', 'Strict No Pet Policy.', 'No Undergrads.', 'Note: there is a one month broker fee', 'Dining Room   Eat-in Kitchen   Hardwood Floors   High Ceiling   Large Rooms   Pantry   Private Deck!', '95 Bus to Sullivan right across the street.', '8 Minute walk to West Medford Train Station', '94 Bus to Davis Square.', 'Haymarket Express Bus to Downtown', 'FEATURES', 'Dining Room', 'Eat-in Kitchen', 'Hardwood Floors', 'High Ceiling', 'Large Rooms', 'Pantry', 'Private Deck!', '**Pricing and Availability subject to Change.', '**', 'Keller Williams ~ Cambridge', 'The Abundant Group', 'CALL & TEXT Friendly', 'Justin Idoine ~ & ~ Carlina Nabatoff', '617-992-0986   or   617-992-0978', 'Prices and Availability are subject to Change.', 'Pictures in the Advertising May NOT be of the actual unit but will represent the unit in its likeness.', 'A Keller Williams Realty Cambridge Team']
